name: Exodia, Master of The Guard
desc: Cannot be Special Summoned. You can Tribute 5 monsters to Tribute Summon (but not Set) this card. If this card Summoned this way destroys a DARK Fiend monster that is owned by your opponent by battle, you win the Duel. This card's ATK/DEF becomes the combined original ATK/DEF of the Tributed monsters.
